elementParameter.name: QUERY
elementParameter.value: "SELECT COUNTS, TRIM(COALESCE(BUSINESS_DTTM, '1900-01-01 00:00:00')) FROM ( SELECT COUNT(*) as COUNTS, TRIM(CAST(SUBSTR(TRIM(CAST(MIN(BUSINESS_DTTM) AS VARCHAR(50))),1,10)||' '||SUBSTR(TRIM(CAST(MIN(BUSINESS_DTTM) AS VARCHAR(50))),11,19) AS VARCHAR(50))) as BUSINESS_DTTM FROM ETL_BUSDATE WHERE PROCESSING_CD=0 AND SRC_SYS_ID = 15 ) AS A"
